{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setlanguage:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setLanguage:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"language","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"language","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The language code (e.g., “en”, “de”, “fr”, “es”) or nil to reset to device language"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Override the device language for Pushwoosh to enable:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sending notifications in a specific language","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Language-based segmentation"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Supporting in-app language switching"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Must be a lowercase two-letter code according to ISO-639-1 standard."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Example","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Support in-app language selection:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class LanguageManager {","","    static let shared = LanguageManager()","","    var currentLanguage: String {","        didSet {","            applyLanguageChange()","        }","    }","","    func applyLanguageChange() {","        \/\/ Update Pushwoosh language for targeted notifications","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","","        \/\/ Update user tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"language\": currentLanguage,","            \"language_changed_date\": Date()","        ])","","        \/\/ Update app UI","        Bundle.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","        NotificationCenter.default.post(name: .languageDidChange, object: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"App language changed to: \\(currentLanguage)\")","    }","","    func resetToDeviceLanguage() {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(nil)","        currentLanguage = Locale.current.languageCode ?? \"en\"","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"“zh” (Chinese), “ja” (Japanese), “ko” (Korean), “ru” (Russian)"}]}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets custom application language for localized notifications."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setLanguage:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setLanguage:","symbolKind":"method","title":"setLanguage:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setLanguage:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setLanguage:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol"